## Visualization Details

- Nodes are rendered as SVG circles with labels.
- Tree edges are drawn dynamically between nodes.
- AVL rotations animate smoothly between states.
- Nodes involved in rotations are temporarily highlighted.
- Layout automatically adjusts as the tree grows.

---

## SQL Integration

SQLite is used to log all tree operations. Each entry stores:
- Operation type
- Inserted value
- Full tree snapshot (JSON)
- Timestamp

This enables future features such as undo/redo, replay, and analytics.

